      <title>越南前政府会计师因盗窃被判处死刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/vietnam-ex-government-accountant-sentenced-to-death-for-theft</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据越南政府网站发布的消息称，河内一家法院判处国家卫生和流行病学研究所前总会计师阮黄 (Nguyen Hoang) 死刑，此前阮黄被判贪污 1520 多亿越南盾（620 万美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/vietnam-ex-government-accountant-sentenced-to-death-for-theft</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 04:45:25 GMT</pubDate>
